          "title": "Scream",
          "year": 1996,
          "note": "Fennessey argued higher for its consistency, then bumped it down."
        },
        {
          "title": "The Omen",
          "year": 1976,
          "note": "Fennessey pushes Omen III; Ryan checked out after two."
        },
        {
          "title": "Poltergeist",
          "year": 1982,
          "note": "The fewest films of the group; last by default, though the first three have fans."
